21 from a diversity, equity, and inclusion initiative under subsection (6) of this
22 section;
23 (6) "Diversity, equity, and inclusion initiative":
24 (a) Means a policy, practice, or procedure designed or implemented to promote
25 or provide differential treatment or benefits to individuals on the basis of
