21 occupation. No voting member at the time of his or her appointment or during the
22 term of his or her service shall be engaged as a professional educator. [Beginning
23 with voting members appointed on or after June 29, 2021, ]Appointments to the
24 group of members representing Supreme Court districts and to the group of at-large
25 members shall[, respectively, shall reflect equal representation of the two (2) sexes,
